2026-05-18T06:16:50.0516164Z 248            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-18T06:16:50.0517010Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-18T06:16:50.0517745Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-18T06:16:50.0518507Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-18T06:16:50.0519659Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-18T06:16:50.0520513Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-18T06:16:50.0521303Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-18T06:16:50.0522010Z 255            preserve via tools:node="merge".
